milestones.description: West Indies have broken the record for most extras conceded in an innings 38 in ODIs, going past Australia's 37
Greenidge and Larry Gomes's 195-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 190 between Chris Tavaré and Allan Lamb
Greenidge has scored 17 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Viv Richards's record
Greenidge has scored 4 hundreds in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Viv Richards's record
Fletcher's 71 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ZIM), surpassing Fletcher's 69
Fletcher has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (28) in an innings in ODIs for ZIM, going past Fletcher's 20
Fletcher and Dave Houghton's 92-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 75 between Iain Butchart and Fletcher
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Greenidge and Larry Gomes's 195-run partnership is WI's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 153 between Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards
Jack Heron and Dave Houghton's 30-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Dave Houghton and Andy Pycroft
Fletcher and Dave Houghton's 92-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Fletcher and Dave Houghton
Fletcher and Peckover's 34-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Robin Brown and Iain Butchart
